OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fdry evening with plenty of sunshine.
OL,7,FCloud filling in during the night with
OL,8,Fsome light rain around the islands by
OL,9,Fdawn.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FCloudy with isolated outbreaks
OL,12,Fof light rain for Argyll, some
OL,13,Fbrighter spells developing later in
OL,14,Fthe day, winds remaining light.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FA
OL,17,Fbright start on Monday but a few
OL,18,Fshowers developing and cloudy at
OL,19,Ftimes. Remaining settled on Tuesday
OL,20,Fand Wednesday with bright or sunny
OL,21,Fspells and light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
